{"tid":1226690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果聽日民陣又話階段性勝利叫大家返屋企","createTime":"2019-06-15T12:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:12:23.000Z","uid":15298,"like":126,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6729d0786c492cbf489d00d0bee7f7b6d58a7d1f","tid":1226690,"uid":15298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"真心一問<br />\n屌你老母依家佢只係暫緩<br />\n遲啲又會推翻出嚟<br />\n早幾日嘅事啲狗又暗地裏捉緊人<br />\n如果聽日民陣又話階段性勝利<br />\n俾啲掌聲自己同埋叫大家返屋企<br />\n有冇巴絲打會上去大台搶咪屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f925fb9f6677cb5619c82e8171268bba85c6dec","tid":1226690,"uid":15298,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"好認真咁問大家<br />\n而家政府拖字訣<br />\n然後靜靜雞咁拉晒啲義士<br />\n假如聽日大家就咁樣返咗屋企<br />\n過多一兩個星期仲會唔會有人可以企出嚟<br />\n定係已經拉晒俾人清算"},{"pid":"8d21e6d9e52cba254b121da926526451efda0000","tid":1226690,"uid":19408,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:55:53.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;唔好意思阻你一陣&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n見到有大陸網站特別支持香港<br />\n仲有埋反送中完整宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhina.wiki/反送支特备条目\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhina.wiki%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E6%94%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%A4%87%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=5fca8ae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhina.wiki/反送支特备条目</a><br />\n反送中宣傳<br />\n<br />\n連大陸人都支持香港，我哋點可以輸？<br />\n6月16日見！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"59e7f72f6a947694c6cdbe535966a9a89b69f602","tid":1226690,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:56:12.000Z","msg":"番你老母"},{"pid":"42eafbb08f4608f1044edac1561a8d2f18ac7880","tid":1226690,"uid":50762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83qMv1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83qMv1Q.png&h=f3bd2cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a70872c1e8207a924c3f342233d863b63483057d","tid":1226690,"uid":4044,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"我覺依家時候真係唔應該再衝，因為12號已經得到世界關注，依家應該繼續係街頭宣傳叫人記得呢件事。"},{"pid":"48c336e17e155483e3cf736eb84a24804ce7b261","tid":1226690,"uid":15298,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"我好認真希望大家諗下<br />\n依家根本係俾機會班犬搜證<br />\n然後拉晒啲義士<br />\n成日見大家話會上大台屌鳩民陣<br />\n如果聽日真係散水會唔會真係有人搶咪講嘢屌鳩民陣"},{"pid":"6298d24d7642f0f945727614632e15a63f763e8a","tid":1226690,"uid":176313,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TqMv2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TqMv2v.jpg&h=1d6b3e7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a677e19d007b1cbfcce8c1c5ffd802725f7b08f","tid":1226690,"uid":15298,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a70872c1e8207a924c3f342233d863b63483057d","tid":1226690,"uid":4044,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"我覺依家時候真係唔應該再衝，因為12號已經得到世界關注，依家應該繼續係街頭宣傳叫人記得呢件事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"唔係話再衝<br />\n而係話唔應該散水返屋企<br />\n依家定性咗件事係暴動<br />\n政府根本係拖緊時間比警犬拉人<br />\n我覺得又去完之後唔應該走"},{"pid":"4d66575aa071e89ca3305ffddb555dedb1185066","tid":1226690,"uid":15298,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"其實大家明唔明乜嘢叫做不撤回不撤退<br />\n依家撤回左啦咩<br />\n星期一大家馬照跑舞照跳<br />\n義士繼續俾人拉<br />\n咁撚樣就走咗去對唔對得住香港人"},{"pid":"4cd01001a62032dc69f7ca16bc517c2626636ca2","tid":1226690,"uid":188437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:11:14.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛又玩挑撥"},{"pid":"f3562d4fd62c4df7015e5c53991152325a977c78","tid":1226690,"uid":47303,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"民陣好似話不滿喎"},{"pid":"cbdddf13f60a8535